


# URIs for the API 

Gets all contacts for a supplies User Id
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/GetAllContacts?uId={userId}

Checks if API is Alive
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/IsAlive

Adds a contact. Body should be in format outlines in the JSON Contract file
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/NewContact

Updates a contact. use the same body JSON format as adding a contact.
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/UpdateContact

Deletes a contact based on the contact Id
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/DeleteContact?cId={conId}

Retrieves a contact's details based on the ContactId
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/GetContactInfo?cId={conId}

Adds a new user via post - JSON Format in the JsonContract file
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/AddUser

Deletes a user via GET
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/DeleteUser?uId={userId}

Get a single user from the database. Returns the ID if successful
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/GetUser

Get single contact
http://oopcontactmanager.azurewebsites.net/ContactManagerService.svc/GetSingleContact?search={searchData}&uId={userId}
